data.title: The Daily Diadem: Princess Marie’s Cabochon Tiara
data.meta_description: Albert Nieboer/DPA Picture Alliance/Alamy Marie of Orleans, wife of Prince Gundakar of Liechtenstein, wears a tiara set with green cabochons -- perhaps jade? -- at a reception following the wedding of Leka of Albania, October
data.text:
Albert Nieboer/DPA Picture Alliance/Alamy

Marie of Orleans, wife of Prince Gundakar of Liechtenstein, wears a tiara set with green cabochons — perhaps jade? — at a reception following the wedding of Leka of Albania, October 2016; the tiara has been in Princess Marie’s collection for several years
